<section id="faq" class="faq">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-heading">Questions, Answered.</h2>
    <div class="faq-list">
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3 class="faq-question">Are you a developer or an agency?</h3>
        <p class="faq-answer">
          No. Steadro is not a traditional agency or a one-off developer. It’s a fractional ecommerce leadership role—I act as the strategic operator who owns the platform and coordinates the specialists.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3 class="faq-question">Do you replace my agency?</h3>
        <p class="faq-answer">
          Not necessarily. Steadro makes your agencies more effective by ensuring they’re focused on the right work, in the right order, and aligned to a clear roadmap.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3 class="faq-question">What size brands is Steadro best for?</h3>
        <p class="faq-answer">
          Typically Shopify brands doing between $100k and $3M annually that are ready to move beyond DIY chaos and build real operational structure.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3 class="faq-question">Will you help us choose apps, tools, and integrations?</h3>
        <p class="faq-answer">
          Yes. A key part of the work is rationalizing your stack and choosing stable, low-tech-debt solutions that fit your stage and goals.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3 class="faq-question">Do you handle execution or just strategy?</h3>
        <p class="faq-answer">
          I own strategy, architecture, and decision-making, and I coordinate the right implementers when needed—developers, agencies, or freelancers. You get senior-level leadership without over-hiring.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% stylesheet %}
  .faq {
    padding: 4rem 24px;
    background-color: var(--bg-primary);
  }
  .container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .section-heading {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  .faq-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .faq-item {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .faq-question {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .faq-answer {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .section-heading {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
{% endstylesheet %}

